{"tid":1329171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中文可以點樣演釋country同nation既區別？","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T06:32:31.000Z","uid":127381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"62012e9a4217d1e05dd460030c088e10c6da051e","tid":1329171,"uid":127381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:31:34.000Z","msg":"英文解釋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.difference.wiki/country-vs-nation/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.difference.wiki%2Fcountry-vs-nation%2Famp%2F&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyh6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=6676030e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.difference.wiki/country-vs-nation/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係country係地域上、政治上層面，而nation比較傾向指一族人既共同語言、歷史、文化。但中文是咪冇分得咁清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再引伸去香港既情況，既然港獨係被政府禁止提倡(Hong Kong as an independent country)，但香港人有共同文化、歷史（英屬時期）同獨特語言（香港廣東話），咁算唔算係形成到一個Hong Kong nation？<br />\n<br />\n利申：皇冠頭出世紙、BNO、香港廣東話係我最引以為榮既核心價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357ada2983c3d134f1c359b95176ae5ef47ed5e7","tid":1329171,"uid":127381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62012e9a4217d1e05dd460030c088e10c6da051e","tid":1329171,"uid":127381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:31:34.000Z","msg":"英文解釋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.difference.wiki/country-vs-nation/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.difference.wiki%2Fcountry-vs-nation%2Famp%2F&d=MciEVzKn1v3nDYmPhzNAyh6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=6676030e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.difference.wiki/country-vs-nation/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n簡單講就係country係地域上、政治上層面，而nation比較傾向指一族人既共同語言、歷史、文化。但中文是咪冇分得咁清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再引伸去香港既情況，既然港獨係被政府禁止提倡(Hong Kong as an independent country)，但香港人有共同文化、歷史（英屬時期）同獨特語言（香港廣東話），咁算唔算係形成到一個Hong Kong nation？<br />\n<br />\n利申：皇冠頭出世紙、BNO、香港廣東話